value.0: As quiet as he is loyal, this brooding young ranger bears unknown burdens upon his shoulders. The Emperor's eyes and ears within the shadows, he misses little and divulges less.
This armor bears the emblem of the Stormcrow family, influential lords of the Northern Reaches.

The last of the Dy'nesh line, this raven-haired elven beauty bears her family's ability to speak with the dead. It is a gift bestowed upon them by the goddess Akhana but jealously reviled by the priesthood. Now she serves the Emperor, finding safety in his shadow.
This suit of armor has been crafted by the superior armorsmiths of the Sharakhan Empire, being both far more durable in combat, and less cumbersome for its wearer.
Masterwork weapons are crafted to be perfectly balanced and weighted, allowing for a far greater control and accuracy in battle.

Stern in countenance and stout of heart, this former slave now serves as the Emperor's secret commander in the field. Part warrior, part ambassador, and part agent of vengeance, he protects the Empire from itself.

Leaving behind a string of gambling debts at every port of call, it is a wonder that this compulsive little halfling has time to serve the Emperor at all. But trust is won across a table's winnings and many a secret gleaned. Perhaps he's a better gambler than he lets on.
